      "short_description": "Provisions a Virtual server instance on IBM Cloud",
      "long_description": "IBM Cloud Virtual Servers for VPC provide fast-provisioned, high-performance instances with network isolation and security. Choose from x86 or s390x profiles to match your compute and memory needs, and manage your resources flexibly .The VSI deployable architecture deploys a Virtual Server Instance (VSI) and its related resources. For more details on Virtual server instance. [refer here](https://cloud.ibm.com/docs/vpc?topic=vpc-about-advanced-virtual-servers) ",
